additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: INGREDIENTS: Dried Tropical Fruits (100%) [(Papaya, Cantaloupe Melon, Pineapple, Coconut Chunks, Peach, Mango, Green Melon, Star Fruit), Sugar, Lime Juice, Acidity Regulator (330), Preservatives (223, 220) (Contains Sulphites)].

description: A tangy and delicious medley of tropical fruits including Papaya, Pineapple, Coconut Chunks, , Mango, Green Melon, Star Fruit selected from around the world. Great addition to any dessert or added to cereals or simply eaten as a snack.
name: Tropical Fruit Mix
